{
  "message": "fuzz(fuse-splice-mount): add 14 structured corpus seeds\n\nCoverage expansion for fuzz_fuse_splice_mount harness:\n- Mount option variations: read-only, allow_other, auto_unmount combinations\n- Worker thread edge cases: 0, 1, 2, 8, random, 4096\n- Fault mode injection: Ok, NotFound, IsDirectory, Format\n- I/O offset edge cases: -1, 0, MAX_FILE_BYTES-1, MAX_FILE_BYTES, i64::MAX\n- Invalid inode numbers (root=1, nonexistent=999)\n- copy_file_range with non-zero flags\n- fsync with datasync=true\n- Zero-length I/O operations\n- Mount options string parsing (ro,allow_other)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
